                  <decoDesc>
                  <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d1"><locus target="#1r" facs="001">Fol. 1r</locus><desc>Four men, one holding a book in one hand and a rod in the other</desc></decoNote>
                  <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d2"><locus target="#9r" facs="009">Fol. 9r</locus><desc>Our Lady <ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1099StMary">St Mary</ref>, crowned, with <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS5684JesusCh">Jesus Christ</persName> seated on her right</desc></decoNote>
                  <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d3"><locus target="#18v" facs="019">Fol. 18v</locus><desc>A woman, holding a handkerchief, before a crowd</desc></decoNote>
                  <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d4"><locus target="#28r" facs="028">Fol. 28r</locus><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1084JesusChrist">JesusChrist</ref> (left) and a man, surrounded by a crowd</desc></decoNote>
                  <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d5"><locus target="#35v" facs="036">Fol. 35v</locus><desc>A woman, holding a child on her back, before a man, surrounded by a crowd</desc></decoNote>
                  <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d6">
                  Decorative designs:
                  <locus target="#7v #25v" facs="008 026">folss. 7v, 25v, </locus> lines of red and black ink;
                  <locus target="#33v" facs="034">33v</locus> multiple full stops.
                  </decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
